{"id":4778,"date":"2017-04-10T10:29:56","date_gmt":"2017-04-10T15:29:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/?page_id=4778"},"modified":"2018-01-17T18:22:52","modified_gmt":"2018-01-17T23:22:52","slug":"egg-cream-home-made-chocolate-soda","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/egg-cream-home-made-chocolate-soda","title":{"rendered":"Egg Cream (Home Made Chocolate Soda)"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3>How to make the perfect Egg Cream!<\/h3>\n<h3>Just for starters an &#8220;Egg Cream&#8221; contains no cream or eggs. \ud83d\ude0e<\/h3>\n<h3>But it does have chocolate and milk!<br \/>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-4782 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322-579x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"545\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322-579x1024.jpg 579w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322-170x300.jpg 170w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322-768x1358.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" \/><\/h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<h3>Get a glass. I like this one.<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-4797 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160448-579x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"545\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160448-579x1024.jpg 579w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160448-170x300.jpg 170w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160448-768x1358.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160448.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<h3>Get some Chocolate Syrup. &#8220;Fox&#8217;s U-bet&#8221; is traditional, but Hershey&#8217;s is just as good!<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-4796 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160534-579x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"545\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160534-579x1024.jpg 579w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160534-170x300.jpg 170w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160534-768x1358.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160534.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<h3>Add 1\/4 Cup of 2% milk and 1 Tablespoon of syrup to the glass.<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-4790 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160946-579x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"545\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160946-579x1024.jpg 579w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160946-170x300.jpg 170w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160946-768x1358.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_160946.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<h3>Mix really well.<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-4789 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161156-579x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"545\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161156-579x1024.jpg 579w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161156-170x300.jpg 170w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161156-768x1358.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161156.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<h3>Fill up to the top with very fizzy, very cold seltzer. I like home made!<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4787 size-large alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161219-579x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"545\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161219-579x1024.jpg 579w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161219-170x300.jpg 170w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161219-768x1358.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161219.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<h3>Enjoy!<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-4782\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322-579x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"545\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322-579x1024.jpg 579w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322-170x300.jpg 170w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322-768x1358.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_20170408_161322.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>It&#8217;s less than 4 Weight &#8220;Watcher&#8217;s Smart Points&#8221; (3.75, actually)<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>How to make the perfect Egg Cream! Just for starters an &#8220;Egg Cream&#8221; contains no cream or eggs. \ud83d\ude0e But it does have chocolate and milk! Get a glass. I like this one. Get some Chocolate Syrup. &#8220;Fox&#8217;s U-bet&#8221; is traditional, but Hershey&#8217;s is just as good! Add 1\/4 Cup of 2% milk and 1 &#8230; <a titl